section.section:
The fees for registration and renewal required under this subsection shall be set by the Division:
In an amount not exceeding $1,200 for a person who is required to purchase a surety bond or file an irrevocable letter of credit or cash under subsection (e) of this section;
In an amount not exceeding $300 for a person who:
Is exempt from the requirement to purchase a surety bond or file an irrevocable letter of credit or cash under subsection (e) of this section; and
Does not meet the requirements of item (iii) of this paragraph; and
In an amount not exceeding $75 for a person who:
Is exempt from the requirement to purchase a surety bond or file an irrevocable letter of credit or cash under subsection (e) of this section;
Does not charge an initiation fee or other fee that is not identified as a payment for specified future services;
Does not contractually obligate a buyer of health club services to pay in advance of the date the services are provided to the buyer; and
Does not collect from a buyer of health club services any payment in advance of the date the services are provided to the buyer.
